<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<sample sampleID="LBb9_00126" version="1.0" type="fixedLength">
<article articleID="LBb9_00126_F001">
<paragraph>
<sentence>　金泥の眼が、窓の朝陽にカ<sampling type="start" />ッと目を<ruby rubyText="む">剥</ruby>いて、光っている。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　<ruby rubyText="おお">大</ruby><ruby rubyText="べし">癋</ruby><ruby rubyText="み">見</ruby>の面である。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「これは、…」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「見おぼえが、あるか？」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「旦那はんの持っといやしたお面どす」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「<ruby rubyText="しか">確</ruby>とそうか？」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「まちがい、おへん」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「そうか」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　百目鬼隼人の口が<ruby rubyText="ゆが">歪</ruby>み気味に嗤った。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「なればこの面が外に落ちておれば、奥羽屋は他出いたしたことになるが…どう致す？」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「落ちてたて、何処にどす？」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「人の斬られておった場所に」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「？</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">…」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「どうじゃ、それでもそなた、奥羽屋は徹宵これに二人で居たと、申しひらきができるか？」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「―」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「どうじゃな？」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　あとの<quote>「どうじゃ」</quote>は奥羽屋へ言っていた。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　染葉はこたえようがない。</sentence>
<sentence>奥羽屋はあくまで団扇で顔をかくしつづけている。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「―女」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　隼人がまた、言った。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi"><quote><sentence>「そもじに今ひとつ、談じ置きたいことがある。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">起て」</sentence>
</quote></sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「え？」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「かまわん。</sentence>
<sentence>いつまでも<ruby rubyText="ぶ">無</ruby><ruby rubyText="しょう">精</ruby>をきめるがような男に膝は無用よ。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">畳へおろし、さ、参ろう」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「何処へ行くのどす？」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「すぐ其処よ」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「？</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">―」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「来いと言うに」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　隼人は、染葉の片手を<ruby rubyText="と">把</ruby>った。</sentence>
<sentence><ruby rubyText="ゆんで">左手</ruby>には差料を<ruby rubyText="さ">提</ruby>げていた。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　手首を引っ張られて、染葉は立たざるを得ない。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「かんにんどっせ」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　膝の奥羽屋へ身をかがめて言い、そっと、腰をずらすと、後頭部を畳の、座布団へのせた。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「染葉」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　団扇の下で英太郎がつぶやいた。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi"><quote>「気をつけて、行けよ」</quote></sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　染葉の身に何が起るかを彼は、知っていたのだろう。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「さ、参ろう」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　隼人がうながして彼女を起たせ、廊下へむかう。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　―途中、</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">「！」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　肘で、やにわに染葉の<ruby rubyText="みぞおち">鳩尾</ruby>へ当て身をくれた。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「ひえっ。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">…」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「ゆるせ。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">…<ruby rubyText="ふ">不</ruby><ruby rubyText="びん">憫</ruby>じゃが、やむを得ぬわ」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　崩れるように、その場へ膝を乱して突っ伏す艶姿を横抱きにすると、隼人は廊下とは反対の出窓の<ruby rubyText="きわ">際</ruby>に寄って、あっという<ruby rubyText="いとま">逞</ruby>も与えず屋根から外へ、女の体を転落させた。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　何か、けざやかな色彩が弧をえがいて、<ruby rubyText="ゆる">弛</ruby>く、奈落へ墜ちるように植込みの緑の繁みの下で、鈍い音を立てていた。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<titleBlock>
<title>
<sentence type="quasi">２</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</title>
</titleBlock>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「やむをえん」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　英太郎のそばへもどると着坐して隼人は言った。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「兵庫が上洛いたすそうな。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">それも尾張侯の内命をうけてな」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「―」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「起きぬか」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　言われて、ゆっくり、上体をおこした奥羽屋英太郎がかおから団扇をはなすと、いつの間に付けたのか、先刻の大癋見の面をかぶっている。</sentence>
<sentence>町人髷に、ちょっと異様なそれは容貌だ。</sentence>
<sentence>帷子の衿もとがはだけ、黒々と彼は胸毛をのぞかせていた。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「さようなものを何故つける？」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「わかりませんか、これが」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「？」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「何処で拾いなされた此の面？」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「大藤幽叟の斬られておった場所よ」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「やはり―」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「ぬ？」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「お手前さまでもお分りにならんのでは、よほど巧妙に打たれておる面ではござろうが、これは、わたしの大癋見ではない。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">偽物です」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「何と？」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「もっとも、どちらが<ruby rubyText="ほんもの">真物</ruby>と言えるかそれは…ハ、ハ、ハ」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　嗤って直ぐ、面をはずすと、</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　<quote>「ご覧なさい、まさしく『古陰』と彫ってはござるがｌ」</quote>―</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　なるほど、あらためて隼人が手にとり、能面の裏をかえすと、『古陰』の銘はあるが今ひとつ、道満一派の<ruby rubyText="しるし">印</ruby>たる朱の斜線が入っていない<sampling type="end" />。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</article>
</sample>
